{"tid":1620443,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"保持冷靜，唔好今日無準備下all in","createTime":"2019-10-04T10:25:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T11:01:03.000Z","uid":706,"like":21,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7a8318f730306b8c2301929a8131ee248563ffaa","tid":1620443,"uid":706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:25:33.000Z","msg":"無長文，只係想提醒大家一樣野<br />\n<br />\non9政府今日宣布得反蒙面法，一定預左民眾會反撲<br />\n今日大家既怒火一定去到頂點，但千祈唔好諗住豁出去同佢搏命，政府一定已經有哂部署，要一網打盡<br />\n<br />\n我唔係要大家散水，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">只係想大家保持理性，如果今日我地係無準備既情況下all in，會好危險<br />\n請記住依個係長期抗爭，唔係一日定輸贏，唔好係毫無準備既情況下豁出去</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n同意請幫手推，好怕大家比怒火沖昏頭腦，依個正正係政府想要既野"},{"pid":"3b2967d9411482b9dd41a1ed38771abe8dbf2026","tid":1620443,"uid":254898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:26:42.000Z","msg":"00 拖到你死<br />\n07 堅持到底<br />\n14 拉埋入冊<br />\n19 無中生有<br />\n歷史總是出奇地相似<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本質沒有改變，性質只有變本加厲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1620380/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1620380/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"ff1fd96448d9fa130b7dacc48eeec396737c1ac5","tid":1620443,"uid":245499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:29:12.000Z","msg":"物資 文宣 交通<br />\n好多野未準備<br />\n除非準備好快閃"},{"pid":"34a70c7ac8658aa6e3137a99c77f5be22c135541","tid":1620443,"uid":706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:32:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e881420564fe2c807d023145107a9f343544a6b4","tid":1620443,"uid":706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:34:59.000Z","msg":"請提醒身邊既人"},{"pid":"0c3581cf4c29f5eab0c56b59ce0de55c47b2ce30","tid":1620443,"uid":706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T10:37:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0b9c0ffffbdec02259a197a7b339703210c816a5